summary:
Business Administration Bachelor`s  Degree PUC / Mentor/ NLP Coach 

31 years leading High Performance Sales Teams in Chile and Abroad with permanent overachievement of goals.
Specialist in designing and implementing innovative business strategies ti open up to new markets 
Mentor and NLP Coach for executives to enhance competences from self-awareness , socioemotional skills , leadership development , effective communication and confidence in decision making.
Courses , Workshops and team intervention through personal development and interactive playful & recreational activities promoting team work

Skills: Sales expertise, negotiation, strategy design, leadership in motivated, high performance and cohesive teams, creativity, proactivity.
